results.name: Signature permutation of a nonrecursive Catalan automorphism: row 65796 of table A089840.
link: A. Karttunen, Prolog-program which illustrates the construction of this and other similar nonrecursive Catalan automorphisms.
Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
program: (Scheme function, destructive implementation of this automorphism acting on S-expressions:) (define (*A123496! s) (cond ((null? s) s) ((and (pair? (car s)) (pair? (caar s))) (*A074680! s) (*A069770! s)) (else (*A074680! s))) s)
xref: Inverse: A123495. a(n) = A069770(A082352(n)). Row 65796 of A089840. Used to construct automorphism *A082358. Cf. A069770 and A074680.
